{"tid":1453050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要讓自己成為散水狗 解散軍","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:14:22.000Z","uid":61672,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a74e16a054a39ffafb951de43020c67aada34a43","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"轉載<br />\n<br />\n如果你冇能力去代入前線嘅心情，就唔好share 前線點樣係鬼點樣唔係鬼。前線打得好，你歡呼；前線出咗事，搵辦法幫手。你只可以做到咁多野，做其他都係多餘、或者反作用。<br />\n<br />\n***<br />\n<br />\n不要讓自己成為散水狗 解散軍<br />\n<br />\n[好重要]<br />\n[解散軍新招]<br />\n[唔該手動轉貼]<br />\n<br />\n關於今日黑警混入示威者捉人一事，衍生出左一個新嘅捉鬼論。<br />\n<br />\n而家開始有BOTH藍屍(特別係藍屍，佢哋不斷喺街坊谷扮黃絲語調)同黃絲「解散軍」就住呢件事想spin掟磚同汽油彈嘅事情落黑警度，話以後見人掟磚放汽油彈就係鬼，叫其他示威者要上前制伏佢。<br />\n<br />\n作為鍵戰嘅各位，<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔可以畀個風向咁spin！<br />\n因為咁樣絕對會增加對前線抗爭者嘅危險！<br />\n前線係有好大可能因為咁畀現場其他跟唔貼嘅抗爭者當黑警般對待。<br />\n<br />\n黑警今時今日下下扑頭、aim頭出催淚彈、橡膠子彈、布袋彈，如果話前線示威者冇掟磚、冇掟汽油彈係「絕。對。冇。本。錢」出來發夢，所以就算係黑警老屈，作為示威者/鍵戰，你老閪都要認左去。<br />\n<br />\n全世界所有國家嘅示威去到某個點都會出動到呢啲武器，所以大家見有人咁spin法，鍵戰一定要阻止！記住，有啲嘢，就算真係畀人屈都唔可以否認！<br />\n<br />\n作為鍵戰如果連承認前線有掟磚掟汽油彈嘅膽量都冇，諗住走精面懶醒目咁去spin，就只會越來越少前線示威者夠膽出去救港！<br />\n<br />\n鳩spin嘅後果就係令自己間接成為解散軍！<br />\n<br />\n#不分化<br />\n#不篤灰<br />\n#不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n#唔該手動轉貼"},{"pid":"cacbca27b655a3bcc3d929a52d46c8ee446f2dc6","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d44246c2a06842ba608532bbcb1331d07885bfc3","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f83d8fa48b3e217028de2583565da78853d9778d","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb9573fdf1b45f859372011b6451c3bdf1456244","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bd735109e67298715b34a8d629ef0f91b0db3b1","tid":1453050,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:09:01.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a>"},{"pid":"e5a37798d01f18ca3ddae1be298fa7efef5e8822","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33bc9f706b45bc0171a031323f70d1b612cba69a","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b7cc682932393c0f021ab5ebab1d62376e29b07","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5e671dfec2b5a38c9f183ea1a13ae123ac0dd00","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df143bd47f80d3b87a0c602f382d0acaf9bb15cb","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab737e444128c696d695b8610254a529d24951d8","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c357db6e9ed1756d4639b1c7e21d2ed9b025b0a","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:11:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be62a9ef2052be852fd95f537e9f800d670c0385","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d43fca2bf0d7960c05b8b043baaf19662700c12f","tid":1453050,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:16:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bfcdea1040d0a5317b8416ea78e1e7e4ca44dfd","tid":1453050,"uid":239615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />派膠？？掟野快過子彈？？情願比人射都唔用腦諗更有效嘅野？？<span style=\"color: r